    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>牌组构筑类Roguelike游戏，但带点小花样！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款有点傻气的卡牌对战游戏！攻击敌人、进行格挡、获取卡牌/遗物、移除卡牌、击杀敌</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >人！不过，你的卡牌不仅能用在自己或敌人身上——</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>卡牌×状态效果！ </strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对自己的出血状态造成伤害，可将其移除或减轻！治疗自己的力量状态，可提升攻击力！治疗</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >敌人的出血状态，让他们死得更快！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317320/extras/5ad18c3a5c5733e33627a24f2fc15523.poster.avif?t=1752517757\" width=408 height=370 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317320/extras/5ad18c3a5c5733e33627a24f2fc15523.webm?t=1752517757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317320/extras/5ad18c3a5c5733e33627a24f2fc15523.mp4?t=1752517757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>卡牌×敌人的意图！</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >粉碎敌人的攻击，最好的防御就是进攻！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317320/extras/69e9fef810a2245a2b3acf7978dae923.poster.avif?t=1752517757\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317320/extras/69e9fef810a2245a2b3acf7978dae923.webm?t=1752517757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317320/extras/69e9fef810a2245a2b3acf7978dae923.mp4?t=1752517757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>卡牌×遗物！</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个能让你把卡牌的效果同时用在所有敌人身上的遗物？那想必是非常适合构筑一击毙命的爆</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发牌组！一个能让你保留卡牌到下一回合的遗物？这样就很方便打出各种连击套路。接下来就</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有你来发掘各种“主动”遗物的潜力了！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317320/extras/2c60f4f881d92f184377630d1c0e77c9.poster.avif?t=1752517757\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317320/extras/2c60f4f881d92f184377630d1c0e77c9.webm?t=1752517757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317320/extras/2c60f4f881d92f184377630d1c0e77c9.mp4?t=1752517757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但最重要的是…… </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>用关键词合成各种卡牌法球！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将各种卡牌相互组合，卡牌中的关键词之间可以产生奇妙的化学反应！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >强效卡牌可以强化卡牌上所有的治疗和状态效果！很适合叠加各种效果！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >低费卡牌消耗的法力值更低！  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不止于此！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这些效果本身就很强大，若与其他卡牌组合，更能爆发惊人威力。围绕强力组合来构筑你的牌</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >组吧。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>初始卡牌</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317320/extras/8a52ef72285bd993d4ebfea83939335e.avif?t=1752517757\" width=325 height=165 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>合成后的卡牌！</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317320/extras/b8d2920003663ce4038642b81beed9fe.avif?t=1752517757\" width=329 height=282 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >真心话时间</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一位热爱卡牌游戏的独立开发者独自完成的小作品，希望你能在这款傻乎乎的小游戏中收</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >获一丝乐趣！</p>",
